rows.label: qst10205_msg001
rows.name: ノポポダイコンが完成したも！(仮)

rows.label: qst10205_msg0002
rows.name:
Grannypon leave seeds to Umama,
say she want to grow more-more
delicious foods...

rows.label: qst10205_msg0003
rows.name:
Dream of Grannypon now come to
fruition on veg patch of Umama!

rows.label: qst10205_msg0004
rows.name:
Umama name this new veg-veg...
Nopopomouli!

rows.label: qst10205_msg0005
rows.name:
Umama know he say he let friends
have first taste, but, see...

rows.label: qst10205_msg0006
rows.name:
Umama could not wait to take bite!
Bite of mouth-drooling deliciousness!
Makes Umama feel ten years younger!

rows.label: qst10205_msg0007
rows.name:
Umama feel Grannypon smiling
from far away...

rows.label: qst10205_msg0008
rows.name:
Could not do this without help
of friends! Many kudos!

rows.label: qst10205_msg0009
rows.name:
However...
Umama not have enough to sell,
still not financially solvent...

rows.label: qst10205_msg0010
rows.name:
Umama sorry, but can only give
friends Nopopomouli as thanks...

rows.label: qst10205_msg0011
rows.name:
Isokay? Is reallyokay?
Oh yes! Umama just remember!

rows.label: qst10205_msg0012
rows.name:
If friends come help again,
Umama give Nopopomouli that
friends help grow!

rows.label: qst10205_msg0013
rows.name:
If friends ever crave Nopopomouli,
come see good old Umama!
